Package: indi-armadillo-platypus-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-armadillo-platypus (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lunatico Armadillo and Platypus Driver.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
